    "description": "你觉得自己够格成为猎鬼师吗？你能将恶灵送回来世吗？你喜欢单独行动，还是团队合作？<br><br>《Ghost Exorcism Inc.》是一款关于驱鬼的恐怖游戏。猎鬼师的任务是清除那些在城堡、豪宅和废弃房屋等地出没的鬼魂。数种超自然的工具可供使用；如EMF K2探测仪、鬼魂分析仪、威胁探测器、监控摄像机等。<br>确定威胁后，你就可以按照给定的驱魔协议，使用中子枪、圣水、熏香等装备超度鬼魂。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人联机</h2>独自游玩或最多6人联机。队友越多，遇到大型地图的几率更高。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/62b939908e4b4c592b8fd3d0f19e7726.poster.avif?t=1688739359\" width=600 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/62b939908e4b4c592b8fd3d0f19e7726.webm?t=1688739359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/62b939908e4b4c592b8fd3d0f19e7726.mp4?t=1688739359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >语音识别</h2>《Ghost Exorcism Inc.》使用你的麦克风与鬼魂沟通。它们会听你说话并理解你的请求，因此请友好交流。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >近距离语音</h2>准备好使用游戏中的近距离语音与队友交流吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/770308cdaab48deaf7c06c636eccb02c.poster.avif?t=1688739359\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/770308cdaab48deaf7c06c636eccb02c.webm?t=1688739359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/770308cdaab48deaf7c06c636eccb02c.mp4?t=1688739359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >任务与进度</h2>成功完成合约以赚取金钱和获得经验。更高等级能购买更先进的设备，从而驱除更多危险的鬼魂。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/34f781c286b4cde0c64c3119cae326a3.poster.avif?t=1688739359\" width=600 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/34f781c286b4cde0c64c3119cae326a3.webm?t=1688739359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/34f781c286b4cde0c64c3119cae326a3.mp4?t=1688739359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种鬼魂类型</h2>不同的鬼魂会有不同的行为和证据。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恶灵袭击</h2>猎鬼绝非易事。鬼魂不希望你在那里，特别是在你要驱除它的情况下。做好充足的防护措施。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/b43bd4d497882e60b7096f8409761ba2.poster.avif?t=1688739359\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/b43bd4d497882e60b7096f8409761ba2.webm?t=1688739359\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1618540/extras/b43bd4d497882e60b7096f8409761ba2.mp4?t=1688739359\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
